    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Essential preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The chassis remains sharp, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers that preserve the model's signature communicative steering and neutral handling balance. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering linear power and the unmistakable metallic rasp of the S54.",
