    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW M2 finished in iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been adult-owned and primarily garaged, showing the pride of ownership throughout. The exterior paint maintains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The interior is exceptionally clean; the black Dakota leather seats with contrast blue stitching are supple, with only very light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the iDrive navigation and Harman Kardon audio system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. It recently underwent a comprehensive multi-point inspection, receiving a fresh oil change and new cabin filters. The tires have substantial tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This M2 offers a pure, engaging driving experience and is ready for its next owner to take the wheel with peace of mind.",
